metadata.name: HUMANOID LOVE  #001
metadata.description:
To love the beautiful thing in the world. love unconditionally and unconditionally. What the world needs most is LOVE. In this collection, I have discussed what humanoids can achieve that we have failed to achieve. The love triangle of all humanoids, male, female, black and white, is in this collection...

I created this collection in 2017 and rearranged in 2022.

1/1 editon

Artist: BioVerses
